OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784233115
OL,3,CRisk of 'Treasury always chickens out'
OL,4,Cmentality at Stormont, MPs told
OL,6,FStormont's Executive needs to "do
OL,7,Ftheir job" and set a budget, Northern
OL,8,FIreland Secretary Hilary Benn has said.
OL,10,FHe gave evidence to MPs after Sir
OL,11,FRobert Chote, chairman of the Northern
OL,12,FIreland Fiscal Council, who said
OL,13,Fcontinued financial bailouts to
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland created the risk of a
OL,15,F"Treasury always chickens out"
OL,16,Fmentality at Stormont.
OL,26,@nD@_OUoD@JO]wD@AOUwD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/15
