OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784233115
OL,3,CRisk of 'Treasury always chickens out'
OL,4,Cmentality at Stormont, MPs told
OL,6,FEarlier this month, Mr Benn and Chief
OL,7,FSecretary to the Treasury Lucy Rigby
OL,8,Fmet leaders of the parties in the
OL,9,Fpower sharing Executive to discuss the
OL,10,Fbudget crisis.
OL,12,FDevolved ministers have failed to
OL,13,Fagree a budget for the current
OL,14,Ffinancial year, with departments
OL,15,Foperating on contingency budgets since
OL,16,FApril.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
