PN,41407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784233115
OL,3,CRisk of 'Treasury always chickens out'
OL,4,Cmentality at Stormont, MPs told
OL,6,FThe Northern Ireland Secretary also
OL,7,Fsaid the department is "still in the
OL,8,Fprocess of establishing the facts
OL,9,Fabout the nature of the likely
OL,10,Foverspend" last year, but added that
OL,11,Fwith Andy Burnham set to take over as
OL,12,Fprime minister next week, the budget
OL,13,Fwould be "the first item on the
OL,14,Fagenda" when he meets the First and
OL,15,Fdeputy First Ministers.
OL,26,@oD@XOUrD@JO]uD@JOUvD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/15
