FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784233115
OL,3,CRisk of 'Treasury always chickens out'
OL,4,Cmentality at Stormont, MPs told
OL,6,F"And then, of course, the new prime
OL,7,Fminister has to look at that alongside
OL,8,Fall of the other pressures that are on
OL,9,Fthe public finances across all the
OL,10,Fareas of government, because it's not
OL,11,Fjust about Northern Ireland."
OL,13,FEarlier in the session Sir Robert
OL,14,Freferred to the phrase "Trump Always
OL,15,FChickens Out" (Taco) used to describe
OL,16,Factivity of some investors in the US
OL,17,Fwho make market predictions based on
OL,18,Fthe assumption that US President
OL,19,FDonald Trump will U-turn on an
OL,20,Fannouncement.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@]O]vD@XOUwD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
