FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784233115
OL,3,CRisk of 'Treasury always chickens out'
OL,4,Cmentality at Stormont, MPs told
OL,6,F"The danger is that the parties play a
OL,7,FTaco trade with the 'Treasury always
OL,8,Fchickens out' or is encouraged to do
OL,9,Fso," he said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@DO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/15
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
