FL,415,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784233115
OL,3,CRisk of 'Treasury always chickens out'
OL,4,Cmentality at Stormont, MPs told
OL,6,F"So there is this inevitable tension
OL,7,Fhere about the desire, obviously, not
OL,8,Fto do anything that would be
OL,9,Fdestabilising and have serious
OL,10,Fconsequences for the citizens of
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland, but on the same
OL,12,Fhand, if you continue to provide that
OL,13,Fsort of resource, which is supposed to
OL,14,Fbe exceptional, but you move in a
OL,15,Fdirection when it looks like it's
OL,16,Fnormalising, that is not setting up
OL,17,Fincentives that are encouraging
OL,18,Fnettles to be grasped."
OL,26,@nD@AOUzD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/15
