OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784233115
OL,3,CRisk of 'Treasury always chickens out'
OL,4,Cmentality at Stormont, MPs told
OL,6,FSir Robert also outlined that if the
OL,7,FUK Government has to legislate for a
OL,8,Fbudget in Northern Ireland "they will
OL,9,Fneed to decide what, if any, strings
OL,10,Fthey wish to attach to that".
OL,26,@pD@\OUrD@\O]
