PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1784233115
OL,3,CRisk of 'Treasury always chickens out'
OL,4,Cmentality at Stormont, MPs told
OL,6,F"If we're in a situation where we have
OL,7,Fa new prime minister, new set of
OL,8,Ftreasury ministers, I'm sure that
OL,9,Fpeople will be telling them that you
OL,10,Fonly have one chance to make a first
OL,11,Fimpression, and if you want to get
OL,12,Faway from the the cycle of the
OL,13,Fexpectation that there will always be
OL,14,Fa bailout coming along, then you
OL,15,Freally only have one chance to do it,"
OL,16,Fhe said.
